00:29:08,539 --> 00:29:10,669
Apa kira-kira kau pernah dengar…

247
00:29:11,834 --> 00:29:13,004
soal "Wonjeong?"

248
00:29:17,631 --> 00:29:18,631
Ya.

249
00:29:19,258 --> 00:29:20,258
Ya.

250
00:29:33,939 --> 00:29:37,529
Jadi, salah satu dari mereka
